Even today, '''the straw hats used in the Daijōsai are made in Fukae and presented to the Imperial Household'''. Additionally, '''Fukae has strong historical ties to the casting of the Imperial Divine Mirror (御神鏡)''', suggesting a connection with '''{{ill|Kagamitsukuri Shrine|ja|鏡作神社|12=draft|12=draft}}''' in '''Shiki District, Tawaramoto Town, Yao'''{{citation needed|date=June 2024}}.
